      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8822780962202990349, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _explanation
      value: 'Platformer controller

        ----------------

        Platformer
        movement; horizontal speed is 125 units per second.

        Horizontal movement
        will be controlled by the [Horizontal] axis.

        Ground check is going
        to use collider GroundCheck, the ground layer mask defines what is considered
        solid ground.

        When there''s no solid ground below character, the
        character will start falling after 0,1s, with a gravity scale of 1,5.

        The
        character''s trajectory can be modified mid-air.

        When in the air,
        the character''s collider will be Player(Player (UnityEngine.BoxCollider2D)),
        and on the ground will be Player(Player (UnityEngine.CapsuleCollider2D)).

        The
        character will jump by holding the [Jump] button.

        The vertical velocity
        will be 150 units/second while jump is pressed, during a maximum of 0,2 seconds.

        Jump
        height will be between 10 to 40 units (from 0,14 to 0,34 seconds to top of
        trajectory).

        This controller also controls some visuals:

        When
        the player intent is to go left, the horizontal scale of this object will
        be inverted.

        Some values will be set on animator Player:

        Horizontal
        velocity will be set to parameter VelocityX.

        Absolute horizontal
        velocity will be set to parameter AbsVelocityX.

        Vertical velocity
        will be set to parameter VelocityY.

        Absolute vertical velocity will
        be set to parameter AbsVelocityY.

        Grounded state will be set to
        parameter IsGrounded.

'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8988164318199248913, guid: 54e157492bc1847d5aed63927d37b536, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: Player
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
